Dear Students,

We are pleased to invite you to an engaging session on *=E2=80=9CCollege to
Corporate =E2=80=93 Data Analyst Role.=E2=80=9D*

The session will be conducted by *Prerna Kamat* and *Priyanshi Jain*, who
bring extensive experience in HR, program execution, and university
engagement initiatives focused on building data-driven career pathways.

During the session, they will share insights on:

   -

   Understanding the *Data Analyst role*
   -

   Career transition from *college to corporate*
   -

   How students can *proactively create opportunities*

*Important:* There is a *possibility that students may be considered for
hiring opportunities during or after the workshop.* Students who attend
will also be *better positioned for similar upcoming roles.*

It is mandatory for students from *non-circuital branches** to attend.*

*Students from circuital branches are also encouraged to attend.*

*Date:* 15th April 2026
*Venue:* Deeksha Sabhaghar
*Time:* 5:00 PM

*Attendance is mandatory and will be strictly recorded.* Students are
expected to be present *on time and actively participate.*

*Note:* Absence from this workshop without a valid reason will be treated
as *serious negligence, similar to the case with the Habile Labs *drive,
and may result in *strict action, including issuance of a red flag.*

We look forward to your participation.

Best regards,
*Team C2C*

--=20
